name: louisiana-speaks-regional-plan-vision-new-growth-areas-utm-zone-15n-nad83-louisiana-recovery-au
notes: This GIS shapefile data illustrates new growth areas included in the Louisiana Speaks Regional Plan Vision. New growth areas include a mix of industrial, single family homes, townhomes, multifamily housing, and local shops that are accessible by transit service and roads. The Louisiana Speaks Regional Plan process study area includes the 35 southernmost parishes of Louisiana.
